OL,7,FA rising proportion of doctors will
OL,8,Fnot blow the whistle over patient
OL,9,Fsafety concerns for fear of
OL,10,Fretribution, leading medics said.
OL,12,FThe British Medical Association (BMA)
OL,13,Fsurveyed doctors from around the UK in
OL,14,F2018 and again in 2024.
OL,16,FA rising proportion said they would
OL,17,Fnot feel confident raising concerns
OL,18,Fabout patient care ` 26% of 1,578
OL,19,Fdoctors in 2024 compared with 10% of
OL,20,Faround 7,900 doctors surveyed in 2018.
