OL,7,FProfessor Philip Banfield, chairman of
OL,8,Fcouncil at the BMA, is set to
OL,9,Fhighlight a culture of "protectionism
OL,10,Frather than accountability".
OL,12,FOn Monday, at the union's national
OL,13,Fannual meeting in Belfast, Prof
OL,14,FBanfield will reference the case of
OL,15,FLucy Letby, where whistleblowers'
OL,16,Fconcerns about the child serial killer
OL,17,Fwere not addressed for months before
OL,18,Fshe was finally taken off frontline
OL,19,Fduties.
